WEBVTT

00:00.979 --> 00:02.278
Hey, there you are.

00:02.479 --> 00:04.279
- I miss you.
- I miss you, too.

00:04.781 --> 00:05.414
Where are you?

00:05.416 --> 00:07.249
I'm in my new city council office.

00:07.251 --> 00:08.750
- No way.
- I know, do you like it?

00:08.752 --> 00:09.751
I love it.

00:09.753 --> 00:11.486
I love it, too.
Check this out.

00:11.988 --> 00:14.756
Here is my wall of inspirational women.

00:15.993 --> 00:17.259
Is that a picture of you?

00:17.261 --> 00:18.794
Yes.
I am big enough to admit

00:18.796 --> 00:21.096
that I am often inspired by myself.

00:21.098 --> 00:24.265
Here are my clocks.
Pawnee and Washington D.C.

00:24.267 --> 00:25.333
Same time zone.

00:25.335 --> 00:26.695
This is the coolest part ever.

00:26.696 --> 00:29.068
I have my own private bathroom.

00:29.169 --> 00:30.068
Occupied!

00:30.069 --> 00:31.468
My God.

00:32.969 --> 00:33.968
Councilman Jamm.

00:34.069 --> 00:35.468
What are you doing in my bathroom?

00:35.519 --> 00:37.468
I don't known if I would call it
<i>your</i> bathroom.

00:37.968 --> 00:40.167
Its only door is in my office.

00:40.168 --> 00:44.071
I think it is crazy that
the most junior city councilor

00:44.073 --> 00:47.108
gets a private bathroom
just because she is a girl.

00:47.110 --> 00:49.744
- Excuse me?
- Let's solve this.

00:49.746 --> 00:50.946
Tell you what I'm going to do.

00:50.947 --> 00:52.880
I'm going to drop my liquids in here,

00:52.882 --> 00:54.315
take my solids down the hall.

00:54.667 --> 00:56.800
- Deal?
- No. No deal.

00:56.802 --> 00:59.270
Fine.
Your loss.

01:01.006 --> 01:02.106
How?

01:05.111 --> 01:09.711
